(vehicles.txt) file is the database where the vehicles and their infos are stored
(u.txt) file is the file which stores all the infos of the user who used the system and what they rent
(rent.txt) is the file which stores all veh that has been rented
(forum.txt) is the file which stores all messages or review wrote by the user of the application

to reduce confusion all vehicles that has been rented, their ids are set to 0 so that in the future no one would rent them again

